BRITTANY AN E-MAIL,

868
00:51:22,347 --> 00:51:24,782
AND SHE WOULD GIVE US
THE NEXT SET OF DIRECTIONS.

869
00:51:24,815 --> 00:51:28,386
BUT WE DECIDED THAT THIS WAS OUR
CHANCE TO SET A TRAP OF OUR OWN

870
00:51:28,419 --> 00:51:31,322
AND FINALLY FIND OUT
WHO SHE REALLY WAS.

871
00:51:38,062 --> 00:51:40,665
[ DRAMATIC MUSIC PLAYS ]

872
00:52:10,628 --> 00:52:12,497
-FAUSTIN!

873
00:52:12,530 --> 00:52:17,935
-OH. UH, I-I HEARD THERE WAS
SOME TROUBLE.

874
00:52:17,968 --> 00:52:20,838
IS EVERYTHING OKAY?

875
00:52:20,871 --> 00:52:21,839
-GUYS.

876
00:52:21,872 --> 00:52:23,641
-SON OF A BITCH.

877
00:52:32,983 --> 00:52:34,919
-[ CHUCKLES ]

878
00:52:34,952 --> 00:52:37,488
ALL RIGHT.

879
00:52:39,457 --> 00:52:41,392
STILL WANT TO KILL ME, CAMERON?

880
00:52:41,426 --> 00:52:43,093
-MM-HMM.

881
00:52:43,127 --> 00:52:46,163
-WHY SHOULDN'T WE JUST TURN YOU
IN TO THE COPS RIGHT NOW, HUH?

882
00:52:46,197 --> 00:52:48,999
-[ LAUGHS ]
TURN ME IN TO T--

883
00:52:49,033 --> 00:52:51,101
