884
00:52:51,135 --> 00:52:52,403
FOR YOU STEALING ACCOUNT NUMBERS

885
00:52:52,437 --> 00:52:55,072
AND TRYING TO CREATE
A FAKE IDENTITY?

886
00:52:55,105 --> 00:52:57,275
I-I DIDN'T DO ANYTHING.

887
00:52:57,308 --> 00:52:58,809
-WHY ARE YOU DOING THIS?

888
00:52:58,843 --> 00:53:01,178
-YOU THINK I LIKE TEACHING
A BUNCH OF KIDS

889
00:53:01,212 --> 00:53:03,814
HIGH SCHOOL SCIENCE?
[ CHUCKLES ]

890
00:53:03,848 --> 00:53:07,952
I'VE HAD THESE
TWO JACKASSES IN MY CLASSES
FOR THE LAST THREE YEARS.

891
00:53:07,985 --> 00:53:12,457
ALL THEY EVER DO IS BLAB ABOUT
THEIR -- THEIR PLANS TO CON
THE SCHOOL.

892
00:53:12,490 --> 00:53:15,893
WELL, I FINALLY DECIDED
TO PUT 'EM TO THE TEST.

893
00:53:15,926 --> 00:53:20,064
SO FAR, THEY'RE A LOT LESS
INCOMPETENT THAN I SUSPECTED.

894
00:53:20,097 --> 00:53:21,632
-WHAT ABOUT THE REST OF US?

895
00:53:22,767 --> 00:53:25,002
-I GUESS I'M JUST LUCKY.

896
00:53:25,035 --> 00:53:27,037
CAMERON.
[ LAUGHS ]

897
00:53:27,071 --> 00:53:29,707
DID YOU REALLY THINK

898
00:53:29,740 --> 00:53:34,044
A STUDENT WHO MISSES MORE
CLASSES THAN A KID WITH LEUKEMIA

899
00:53:34,078 --> 00:53:39,484
[LAUGHS] ASKING ME TO MAKE UP
A LAB WOULDN'T BE A RED FLAG?

900
00:53:39,517 --> 00:53:42,620
YOU GUYS DIDN'T EVEN COVER
YOUR TRACKS.

901
00:53:42,653 --> 00:53:45,089
I WAS JUST THE ONLY ONE
WHO PAID ATTENTION.

902
00:53:45,122 --> 00:53:47,425
-NO, WE'RE DONE WITH YOU.
OKAY?

903
00:53:47,458 --> 00:53:49,494
NO MATTER WHAT YOU SAY,
YOU'RE JUST AS GUILTY AS US.

904
00:53:49,527 --> 00:53:52,430
AND IF YOU DON'T STOP SOON...
WE'RE ALL GONNA GET CAUGHT.

905
00:53:52,463 --> 00:53:54,532
-THAT'S NOT HOW I SEE IT.
-YEAH?

906
00:53:54,565 --> 00:53:56,267
-NO.

907
00:53:56,301 --> 00:53:59,036
YOU SEE, I DON'T HAVE
A LOT TO LOSE.

908
00:53:59,069 --> 00:54:01,939
[ CHUCKLES ]

909
00:54:01,972 --> 00:54:06,711
THIS -- THIS IS MY FUTURE.

910
00:54:06,744 --> 00:54:12,283
SURROUNDED BY A BUNCH
OF...ENTITLED BRATS.

911
00:54:12,317 --> 00:54:14,118
BUT YOUR FUTURES...

912
00:54:15,320 --> 00:54:18,055
...THEY HAVEN'T
EVEN STARTED YET.

913
00:54:18,088 --> 00:54:21,992
GETTING CAUGHT TRYING TO DEFRAUD
A STATE-FUNDED INSTITUTION...

914
00:54:22,793 --> 00:54:25,896
...IS A NICE WAY TO MAKE SURE
THEY NEVER DO.

915
00:54:25,930 --> 00:54:28,699
-RICKY! RICKY.

916
00:54:29,934 --> 00:54:33,070
-NO MORE.

917
00:54:35,306 --> 00:54:37,575
[ SCREAMS ]

918
00:54:42,079 --> 00:54:45,149
-WHAT DO YOU WANT US TO DO?

919
00:54:45,182 --> 00:54:49,854
-I JUST THINK THAT...
BRITTANY TAMMAND

920
00:54:49,887 --> 00:54:53,824
IS OWED A LOT OF MONEY
BY THIS SCHOOL.

921
00:54:53,858 --> 00:54:56,861
AND SINCE SHE'S NOT AROUND
TO COLLECT IT,

922
00:54:56,894 --> 00:54:59,296
I THINK I WILL.

923
00:54:59,330 --> 00:55:01,599
-WHAT THE HELL
ARE YOU TALKING ABOUT?

924
00:55:01,632 --> 00:55:05,870
-THE FUNDRAISER
AFTER SHE OFFED HERSELF...

925
00:55:05,903 --> 00:55:09,774
THEY COLLECTED A LOT MORE
THAN THE $60,000 THEY DONATED.

926
00:55:09,807 --> 00:55:11,275
[ LAUGHS ]

927
00:55:11,308 --> 00:55:15,380
AND YOU'RE GONNA GET IT FOR ME.

928
00:55:15,413 --> 00:55:16,914
ALEX ISN'T THE ONLY ONE

929
00:55:16,947 --> 00:55:19,950
POKING AROUND
ON THE PRINCIPAL'S COMPUTER.

930
00:55:19,984 --> 00:55:21,285
-HOW MUCH IS IT?

931
00:55:21,318 --> 00:55:24,288
-ALMOST HALF A MILLION DOLLARS.

932
00:55:24,321 --> 00:55:26,757
BUT DON'T -- DON'T WORRY.

933
00:55:26,791 --> 00:55:30,027
THERE'S A VERY LOW CHANCE
OF BEING TURNED IN FOR
STEALING STOLEN MONEY.

934
00:55:30,060 --> 00:55:33,330
BUT JUST IN CASE, I'M GONNA
LET YOU TAKE CARE OF IT.

935
00:55:33,364 --> 00:55:35,433
HAND IT OVER.

936
00:55:36,300 --> 00:55:38,403
AND THEN YOU'LL NEVER
HEAR FROM ME AGAIN.

937
00:55:38,436 --> 00:55:41,772
-HOW EXACTLY ARE WE
SUPPOSED TO DO THAT?

938
00:55:43,674 --> 00:55:47,478
-I -- I'VE GIVEN YOU
ALL THE HELP I CAN.

939
00:55:47,512 --> 00:55:51,215
YOUR FATHER'S A BUSINESSMAN.

940
00:55:51,248 --> 00:55:54,351
FIGURE IT OUT.

941
00:55:58,255 --> 00:56:00,425
[ DOOR OPENS ]
-WHAT?

942
00:56:01,659 --> 00:56:03,961
-MISS SEDGEWICK.

943
00:56:03,994 --> 00:56:06,731
-EXCUSE ME, ALEX.

944
00:56:11,669 --> 00:56:14,338
[ DOOR OPENS ]

945
00:56:20,077 --> 00:56:21,546
-THERE'S NEWS FROM THE HOSPITAL.

946
00:56:21,579 --> 00:56:22,880
-YOU EMBEZZLED MONEY --

947
00:56:22,913 --> 00:56:24,749
[ POLICE RADIO CHATTER ]

948
00:56:24,782 --> 00:56:28,519
YOU EMBEZZLED MONEY
FROM A CHARITY FUND
FOR A SUICIDE VICTIM.

949
00:56:28,553 --> 00:56:31,055
IF THIS LEAKS, OUR SCHOOL SYSTEM
WILL NEVER RECOVER.

950
00:56:31,088 --> 00:56:34,291
YOU BETTER BE THANKING GOD THAT
MOST OF THE PEOPLE THAT KNOW
ABOUT THIS ARE DEAD.

951
00:56:34,324 --> 00:56:37,428
DO WE HAVE TO WORRY
ABOUT BRITTANY'S FAMILY?
-THEY'RE ALL TRAILER TRASH.

952
00:56:37,462 --> 00:56:39,296
I MEAN,
BETWEEN THE ABUSE AT HOME

953
00:56:39,329 --> 00:56:41,331
AND HER SCREWING ANY BOY
THAT SMILED AT HER,

954
00:56:41,365 --> 00:56:43,868
IT'S A MIRACLE SHE DIDN'T --

955
00:56:43,901 --> 00:56:47,004
LOOK, I THOUGHT IF THE SCHOOL
HELD ON TO THE FUNDS,

956
00:56:47,037 --> 00:56:49,674
MAYBE WE COULD MAKE
SOME GOOD COME OF IT.
-[ SCOFFS ]

957
00:56:49,707 --> 00:56:54,712
-IF ANYBODY FINDS OUT ABOUT
THIS, ALEX THOMAS IS GONNA BE
THE LEAST OF YOUR WORRIES.

958
00:56:54,745 --> 00:56:56,614
DO YOU HAVE BRITTANY'S FILES?

959
00:56:56,647 --> 00:56:59,884
-CHILD SERVICES TOOK OUR HARD
COPIES RIGHT AFTER THE SUICIDE,

960
00:56:59,917 --> 00:57:01,852
BUT OUR --
OUR STATE RECORDS HAVE --

961
00:57:01,886 --> 00:57:03,020
-I WANT THEM RIGHT NOW!

962
00:57:03,053 --> 00:57:07,057
-OKAY.
-[ SLAMS LOCKER ]

963
00:57:07,091 --> 00:57:09,627
[ SIGHS ]

964
00:57:12,129 --> 00:57:14,364
-JACK IS, UM --

965
00:57:14,398 --> 00:57:17,535
HE'S TAKEN A TURN FOR THE WORSE.

966
00:57:17,568 --> 00:57:20,605
-THE SOONER THIS ALL DISAPPEARS,
THE BETTER.

967
00:57:20,638 --> 00:57:22,372
-[ SIGHS ]
WHAT ARE YOU GONNA DO?

968
00:57:22,406 --> 00:57:24,141
-I'M GONNA MAKE SURE
THAT WHATEVER HAPPENED,

969
00:57:24,174 --> 00:57:26,577
ALEX THOMAS TAKES TO THE GRAVE.

970
00:57:26,611 --> 00:57:28,245
HOW'S THAT TRANSFER GOING?

971
00:57:28,278 --> 00:57:30,280
-PAPERWORK SHOULD BE READY SOON.
-GREAT.

972
00:57:30,314 --> 00:57:31,982
YOU WANT TO CHECK ON THAT
FOR ME?

973
00:57:32,016 --> 00:57:34,251
-OKAY.

974
00:57:42,092 --> 00:57:44,128
[ DOOR CLOSES ]

975
00:57:44,161 --> 00:57:46,631
-YOU KNOW, I THINK
I HAVE THE RIGHT TO KNOW WHEN
MY PAPERWORK WILL BE READY.

976
00:57:46,664 --> 00:57:48,599
-I KNOW.
[ ZIPPER UNZIPS ]

977
00:57:48,633 --> 00:57:53,604
NO ONE CAN TELL THE FUTURE,
ALEX.

978
00:57:55,773 --> 00:57:56,641
GUM?

979
00:57:56,674 --> 00:57:58,308
-NO, THANK YOU.
-NO?

980
00:57:58,342 --> 00:58:00,177
OKAY.
[ ZIPPER ZIPS ]

981
00:58:00,210 --> 00:58:04,381
SO, WHY DON'T YOU, UM, TELL ME

982
00:58:04,414 --> 00:58:08,085
WHAT HAPPENED AFTER FAUSTIN
TALKED TO YOU

983
00:58:08,118 --> 00:58:10,721
AT THE FOOTBALL GAME?

984
00:58:10,755 --> 00:58:14,124
-UH, AFTER THE FOOTBALL GAME,

985
00:58:14,158 --> 00:58:18,563
UH, I GUESS WE ALL WENT BACK
TO OUR DAILY LIVES.

986
00:58:23,701 --> 00:58:25,670
-FOCUS.

987
00:58:31,809 --> 00:58:35,145
-WHERE'S RICKY TODAY?
EVERYTHING OKAY?

988
00:58:36,146 --> 00:58:41,085
-HE -- HE MAY HAVE BEEN PUSHED
INTO ONCOMING TRAFFIC
ON HIS WAY TO SCHOOL.

989
00:58:42,452 --> 00:58:44,555
-[ LAUGHS ]

990
00:58:44,589 --> 00:58:47,424
-WELL, LET ME KNOW
IF YOU TALK TO HIM.

991
00:58:47,457 --> 00:58:50,494
HE CAN'T AFFORD TO MISS
TOO MANY CLASSES.

992
00:58:55,299 --> 00:58:57,467
[ KNOCK ON DOOR ]

993
00:58:59,336 --> 00:59:01,271
-IS RICKY HOME?

994
00:59:01,305 --> 00:59:03,173
-HE'S NOT WELL.

995
00:59:03,207 --> 00:59:06,811
-NEITHER AM I.
I STILL NEED TO TALK TO HIM.

996
00:59:09,146 --> 00:59:12,116
WATCH OUT.

997
00:59:12,149 --> 00:59:15,119
-[ SPEAKING RUSSIAN ]

998
00:59:22,259 --> 00:59:25,262
I'M NOT GOING TO SCHOOL
TO BE PUSHED AROUND BY
THAT ASSHOLE, MAN.

999
00:59:25,295 --> 00:59:28,032
-WE DON'T HAVE
A LOT OF OPTIONS, RICKY.
-THAT'S WHAT YOU THINK.

1000
00:59:28,065 --> 00:59:30,500
BECAUSE IF YOU DIDN'T ACTUALLY
KNOW, WE CAN DO SOMETHING

1001
00:59:30,534 --> 00:59:33,037
IF YOU USE
THAT LITTLE BRAIN OF YOURS.
-YOU MEAN, YOU WANT TO --

1002
00:59:33,070 --> 00:59:36,540
YOU WANT TO DO
SOMETHING ABOUT IT?
-NO. ARE YOU CRAZY?

1003
00:59:36,573 --> 00:59:39,409
I MEAN, WE DO WHAT WE SHOULD
HAVE DONE WEEKS AGO.
WE TELL THE POLICE.

1004
00:59:39,443 --> 00:59:40,978
-ARE YOU CRAZY?
YOU HEARD FAUSTIN.

1005
00:59:41,011 --> 00:59:43,681
HE HASN'T DONE ANYTHING ILLEGAL,
RICKY.

1006
00:59:43,714 --> 00:59:45,249
WE'RE GONNA GET IN TROUBLE.
COME ON.

1007
00:59:45,282 --> 00:59:46,684
-SO, WE MAKE A DEAL.

1008
00:59:46,717 --> 00:59:48,819
-A DEAL?
-YEAH.

1009
00:59:48,853 --> 00:59:51,756
-GUILTY UNTIL PROVEN INNOCENT.
I'M NOT GOING TO JAIL FOR YOU,

1010
00:59:51,789 --> 00:59:54,058
YOUR MOMS, YOUR DAD,
THEM LITTLE KIDS, NOBODY!

1011
00:59:54,091 --> 00:59:56,661
-OKAY, LOOK.
-STOP ACTING LIKE
A LITTLE BITCH RIGHT NOW!

1012
00:59:56,694 --> 01:00:01,565
HEY! MY PARENTS DIDN'T MOVE HERE
TO BE PUSHED AROUND BY
SOME BULLY, OKAY?

1013
01:00:01,598 --> 01:00:04,468
I'M GONNA DO WHAT'S RIGHT!

1014
01:00:04,501 --> 01:00:07,638
AND YOU CAN DO
WHATEVER YOU WANT, OKAY?

1015
01:00:07,672 --> 01:00:09,139
YOU CAN GO NOW.

1016
01:00:09,173 --> 01:00:11,842
-CAMERON CALLED US ALL
AND TOLD US ABOUT RICKY.

1017
01:00:11,876 --> 01:00:16,647
EVERYONE WAS...SO ON EDGE.

1018
01:00:21,351 --> 01:00:24,689
YOU KNOW, I THOUGHT THAT WE
SHOULD LET HIM OFF THE HOOK,

1019
01:00:24,722 --> 01:00:27,992
BUT CAMERON DIDN'T THINK IT
WOULD BE ENOUGH.

1020
01:00:30,027 --> 01:00:32,596
-FAUSTIN.

1021
01:00:32,629 --> 01:00:34,699
-CAMERON, YOU SCARED ME.

1022
01:00:34,732 --> 01:00:37,001
-YEAH?
-YEAH.

1023
01:00:37,034 --> 01:00:42,272
-IT MUST SUCK TO BE YOU.

1024
01:00:42,306 --> 01:00:44,641
-YES?

1025
01:00:44,675 --> 01:00:47,511
-RICKY'S TALKING ABOUT
GOING TO THE COPS.

1026
01:00:47,544 --> 01:00:50,915
WE DON'T KNOW WHAT TO DO.

1027
01:00:50,948 --> 01:00:52,917
-OH.

1028
01:00:52,950 --> 01:00:55,319
UH, OKAY.

1029
01:00:55,352 --> 01:00:57,387
OKAY, I'LL TAKE CARE OF THAT.

1030
01:00:57,421 --> 01:00:59,589
DON'T WORRY, I'LL TRY NOT
TO HURT HIM.

1031
01:00:59,623 --> 01:01:01,726
-I DON'T CARE WHAT YOU DO.

1032
01:01:02,793 --> 01:01:06,931
-YOU DID THE SMART THING.

1033
01:01:06,964 --> 01:01:10,835
-YOU KNOW, YOU KNOW,
AFTER ALL THIS IS OVER,

1034
01:01:10,868 --> 01:01:14,705
I PLAN ON DOING
A LOT OF SMART THINGS.

1035
01:01:14,739 --> 01:01:17,908
I'D WATCH MY BACK, IF I WAS YOU.

1036
01:01:22,079 --> 01:01:24,481
-[ LAUGHS ]

1037
01:01:29,754 --> 01:01:32,890
-THE NEXT DAY AFTER SCHOOL,
I WENT TO TALK TO RICKY.

1038
01:01:34,792 --> 01:01:37,527
HE WAS DEAD TO CAMERON
AND THE OTHERS,

1039
01:01:37,561 --> 01:01:40,030
BUT I THOUGHT
HE DESERVED A WARNING.

1040
01:01:40,064 --> 01:01:42,132
YOU KNOW, MAYBE IF HE KNEW
THAT FAUSTIN WAS AFTER HIM,

1041
01:01:42,166 --> 01:01:45,770
THEN HE WOULD RECONSIDER
GOING TO THE POLICE.

1042
01:01:49,473 --> 01:01:51,641
-RICKY!

1043
01:01:56,213 --> 01:01:58,248
WHAT'S GOING ON?

1044
01:01:58,282 --> 01:02:00,550
-WE'VE BEEN EVICTED.

1045
01:02:00,584 --> 01:02:03,653
-EVICTED, WHY?

1046
01:02:05,555 --> 01:02:08,959
-WELL, UH,
WE WERE REPORTED

1047
01:02:08,993 --> 01:02:12,662
FOR HAVING SEVEN PEOPLE
IN A TWO-PERSON UNIT.

1048
01:02:12,696 --> 01:02:15,232
-WHERE ARE YOU GOING?

1049
01:02:15,265 --> 01:02:18,803
-MY FATHER HAS FRIENDS
IN CLEVELAND.

1050
01:02:18,836 --> 01:02:20,938
WE WILL TRY THERE.

1051
01:02:24,574 --> 01:02:27,244
I SHOULD HAVE NEVER DONE ANY OF
THIS IN THE FIRST PLACE, HUH?

1052
01:02:30,414 --> 01:02:33,183
-I'M SORRY.
-YEAH.

1053
01:02:33,217 --> 01:02:34,651
BEING FORCED TO MOVE

1054
01:02:34,684 --> 01:02:37,754
IS BETTER THAN MY PARENTS
SEEING ME IN JAIL, RIGHT?

1055
01:02:37,788 --> 01:02:40,190
-[ SPEAKING RUSSIAN ]

1056
01:02:40,224 --> 01:02:41,225
-HEY!

1057
01:02:41,258 --> 01:02:43,560
[ SPEAKING RUSSIAN ]

1058
01:02:47,731 --> 01:02:49,967
-FOR A MOMENT, I ENVIED RICKY.

1059
01:02:50,000 --> 01:02:52,970
I MEAN, HIS LIFE
WAS TURNED UPSIDE DOWN,

1060
01:02:53,003 --> 01:02:59,043
BUT...HE DIDN'T HAVE TO WORRY
ABOUT FAUSTIN ANYMORE.

1061
01:02:59,076 --> 01:03:01,711
FOR HIM...

1062
01:03:01,745 --> 01:03:05,682
IT WAS OVER.

1063
01:03:05,715 --> 01:03:07,784
I THOUGHT ABOUT TELLING
THE OTHERS

1064
01:03:07,818 --> 01:03:09,519
THAT I WANTED TO GO
TO THE POLICE, TOO.

1065
01:03:09,553 --> 01:03:15,259
YOU KNOW, FORCE HIM TO FIND
A WAY TO GET ME OFF THE TEAM.

1066
01:03:15,292 --> 01:03:19,930
BUT THEN I REMEMBERED THAT RICKY
HAD A FAMILY TO FALL BACK ON.

1067
01:03:21,631 --> 01:03:23,733
IF YOU'RE A PROBLEM
IN FOSTER CARE,

1068
01:03:23,767 --> 01:03:25,903
THEY NEVER SEND YOU
TO A BETTER PLACE.

1069
01:03:34,578 --> 01:03:37,481
-I HOPE YOU HAVE
GOOD NEWS FOR ME.

1070
01:03:37,514 --> 01:03:40,885
-WE'VE BEEN WORKING ON IT
ALL WEEK.

1071
01:03:40,918 --> 01:03:42,953
IT'S IMPOSSIBLE.
-[ LAUGHS ]

1072
01:03:42,987 --> 01:03:45,055
-HASN'T THE STAFF OF ARCHER
TAUGHT YOU ANYTHING?

1073
01:03:45,089 --> 01:03:47,524
NOTHING IS IMPOSSIBLE.
-WE'VE TRIED EVERYTHING.

1074
01:03:47,557 --> 01:03:50,127
SHORT OF BEING COMPUTER HACKERS
OR HYPNOTISTS,

1075
01:03:50,160 --> 01:03:54,098
THERE'S NO WAY WE'RE GONNA GET
THE INFORMATION WE NEED WITHOUT
SOMEONE FLAT-OUT TELLING US.

1076
01:03:54,131 --> 01:03:56,400
-ARE YOU REALLY WILLING
TO TURN ALL OF US IN?

1077
01:03:57,667 --> 01:04:00,004
-MM. NO.

1078
01:04:02,106 --> 01:04:06,843
BUT...I WILL DO EVERYTHING
HUMANLY POSSIBLE

1079
01:04:06,877 --> 01:04:09,613
TO RUIN YOUR LIVES.

1080
01:04:09,646 --> 01:04:12,249
YEAH.

1081
01:04:12,282 --> 01:04:14,351
I'LL DEVOTE MYSELF TO IT.

1082
01:04:14,384 --> 01:04:18,655
I WILL CALL PROSPECTIVE COLLEGES
AND MAKE SURE YOU DON'T GET IN.

1083
01:04:18,688 --> 01:04:21,725
AS FOR YOUR YOUNGER SIBLINGS,

1084
01:04:21,758 --> 01:04:26,730
I'LL MAKE SURE ARCHER
IS A LIVING HELL.

1085
01:04:26,763 --> 01:04:29,833
I'LL GO AFTER YOUR PARENTS.

1086
01:04:30,600 --> 01:04:32,169
LOOK AT RICKY.

1087
01:04:35,239 --> 01:04:39,944
ARE YOU WILLING TO LET
YOUR FAMILIES GO THROUGH THAT?

1088
01:04:41,678 --> 01:04:43,981
HOW ABOUT SOMETHING WORSE?

1089
01:04:44,014 --> 01:04:47,417
JUST FIGURE IT OUT!

1090
01:04:50,420 --> 01:04:53,457
-[ CRYING ]

1091
01:04:53,490 --> 01:04:57,027
[ DOOR OPENS, CLOSES ]

1092
01:05:04,401 --> 01:05:06,170
[ SIGHS ]

1093
01:05:06,203 --> 01:05:07,737
-I DECIDED TO GO THROUGH
WITH THIS

1094
01:05:07,771 --> 01:05:10,874
BECAUSE I SAW HOW RESOURCEFUL
YOU ARE.

1095
01:05:10,907 --> 01:05:13,410
IF I WERE YOU...

1096
01:05:14,744 --> 01:05:16,981
...I WOULD THINK HARDER

1097
01:05:17,014 --> 01:05:21,851
OR PREPARE TO SUFFER
INCONCEIVABLE CONSEQUENCES.

1098
01:05:26,323 --> 01:05:29,026
[ DOOR OPENS ]

1099
01:05:35,632 --> 01:05:37,734
-WE GOT TO THINK OF SOMETHING.
WE GOT TO THINK QUICK.

1100
01:05:37,767 --> 01:05:40,270
-MAYBE DONATO HAS THE PASSWORDS
WRITTEN DOWN SOMEWHERE.

1101
01:05:40,304 --> 01:05:42,439
YOU KNOW, YOU COULD
CALL ANOTHER MEETING.
-ARE YOU RETARDED?!

1102
01:05:42,472 --> 01:05:45,175
-NOBODY HAS PASSWORDS
TO THEIR BANK ACCOUNTS
JUST SITTING AROUND, ALEX!

1103
01:05:45,209 --> 01:05:47,377
-WHAT IF WE BLACKMAIL HIM?
-BLACKMAIL THE PRINCIPAL?

1104
01:05:47,411 --> 01:05:50,647
-YEAH. WE TELL HIM THAT WE
KNOW HE TOOK THE MONEY

1105
01:05:50,680 --> 01:05:53,383
FROM BRITTANY TAMMAND'S STUPID
SCHOOL FUND, AND WE FORCE HIM
TO HAND IT OVER.

1106
01:05:53,417 --> 01:05:56,353
-HE WOULD JUST HIDE THE MONEY
AND HAVE US ARRESTED.

1107
01:05:58,622 --> 01:06:00,557
-WHAT IF WE TAKE OUT FAUSTIN?

1108
01:06:00,590 --> 01:06:01,725
-WHAT?
-ARE YOU CRAZY?

1109
01:06:01,758 --> 01:06:04,894
WE'RE NOT CRIMINALS.

1110
01:06:04,928 --> 01:06:08,432
-AFTER ALL THIS SHIT,
YOU'RE NOT A CRIMINAL?!

1111
01:06:08,465 --> 01:06:11,568
WHAT IF I WAIT IN THE BACK
OF THIS CAR AND I SLIT OPEN
HIS THROAT?

1112
01:06:11,601 --> 01:06:13,003
-STOP!
-HOW'S THAT FOR A PLAN?!

1113
01:06:13,037 --> 01:06:15,072
-STOP, CAMERON!
YOU'RE TALKING ABOUT SOMETHING

1114
01:06:15,105 --> 01:06:16,940
THAT COULD GET US
LIFE IN PRISON.

1115
01:06:16,973 --> 01:06:21,078
-NOT IF WE DON'T GET CAUGHT.
-PEOPLE LIKE YOU ALWAYS
GET CAUGHT.

1116
01:06:22,412 --> 01:06:24,114
[ LAUGHS ]

1117
01:06:24,148 --> 01:06:27,984
-AND PIECES OF SHIT LIKE YOU
THREE WILL ALWAYS BE VICTIMS.

1118
01:06:28,018 --> 01:06:30,087
MOVE.
GET OUT OF MY WAY.

1119
01:06:30,120 --> 01:06:32,222
-CAMERON, COME ON.
-SCREW OFF, JACK.

1120
01:06:32,256 --> 01:06:33,790
-ALL RIGHT, FINE, BAIL ON US!

1121
01:06:33,823 --> 01:06:36,126
[ ENGINE TURNS OVER ]

1122
01:06:36,160 --> 01:06:37,994
[ HIP-HOP MUSIC PLAYS ]

1123
01:06:47,404 --> 01:06:50,674
-MAYBE WE JUST...
TALK TO OUR PARENTS

1124
01:06:50,707 --> 01:06:52,742
AND SEE IF THEY'RE WILLING
TO PAY FAUSTIN OFF.
-NO, NO.

1125
01:06:52,776 --> 01:06:54,944
IF MY PARENTS FIND OUT --
-YOU THINK YOUR CONSTANT
BITCHING

1126
01:06:54,978 --> 01:06:57,847
IS GONNA SOLVE
ANY PROBLEMS, CARLA?!

1127
01:06:59,516 --> 01:07:02,086
[ VEHICLE DOOR CLOSES ]

1128
01:07:02,119 --> 01:07:04,421
[ ENGINE TURNS OVER ]

1129
01:07:07,824 --> 01:07:10,160
[ VEHICLE DEPARTS ]
-[ COUGHING ]

1130
01:07:10,194 --> 01:07:12,196
-WE KNEW WHAT WE HAD TO DO.

1131
01:07:12,229 --> 01:07:14,931
WE JUST HAD NO IDEA
HOW TO DO IT.

1132
01:07:16,666 --> 01:07:18,402
WE'RE IN HIGH SCHOOL.

1133
01:07:18,435 --> 01:07:21,171
HOW ARE WE SUPPOSED TO KNOW
HOW TO TRANSFER MONEY

1134
01:07:21,205 --> 01:07:24,108
FROM A SCHOOL BANK ACCOUNT
TO OUR FAKE ONE?

1135
01:07:24,141 --> 01:07:26,876
EVERYONE WAS JUST FREAKED OUT,

1136
01:07:26,910 --> 01:07:29,879
SOME OF US MORE THAN OTHERS.

1137
01:07:29,913 --> 01:07:31,315
-NEW DEAL.

1138
01:07:31,348 --> 01:07:34,318
1933 TO 1938.

1139
01:07:34,351 --> 01:07:37,020
NOW, THIS IS A SERIES OF
DOMESTIC ECONOMIC PROGRAMS

1140
01:07:37,053 --> 01:07:38,688
DEVELOPED BY FDR IN AN EFFORT

1141
01:07:38,722 --> 01:07:41,191
TO COMBAT THE GREAT DEPRESSION.
-MR. -- MR. CONNOR?

1142
01:07:41,225 --> 01:07:46,230
-YES, CARLA? CARLA, WHAT?
-MR. CONNOR -- MR. CONNOR,

1143
01:07:46,263 --> 01:07:49,266
I REALLY -- I NEED TO GO
TO THE BATH--

1144
01:07:49,299 --> 01:07:52,536
-ARE YOU OKAY?
[ DOOR OPENS ]

1145
01:07:53,470 --> 01:07:55,439
WHOA, WHOA, WHOA.
WHOA, WHOA, JACK, NO.

1146
01:07:55,472 --> 01:07:57,374
I NEED YOU TO SIT DOWN.
-I'M MAKING SURE SHE'S OKAY!

1147
01:07:57,407 --> 01:08:00,677
-HEY, DON'T YOU -- GET BACK HERE
AND SIT DOWN, JACK!

1148
01:08:00,710 --> 01:08:01,811
-SORRY, SIR.
-NO!

1149
01:08:01,845 --> 01:08:03,947
OKAY, THAT'S -- YOU CAN'T --

1150
01:08:03,980 --> 01:08:06,250
-[ PANTING ]

1151
01:08:08,585 --> 01:08:09,919
-CARLA!

1152
01:08:14,057 --> 01:08:15,625
-[ RETCHING ]

1153
01:08:15,659 --> 01:08:17,327
[ COUGHS ]

1154
01:08:17,361 --> 01:08:19,496
-CAR-- OH, SHIT.

1155
01:08:21,898 --> 01:08:24,067
-OPEN THE DOOR, CARLA!
OPEN THE DOOR!

1156
01:08:24,100 --> 01:08:26,636
-WHAT YOUR FEET.

1157
01:08:26,670 --> 01:08:29,105
-I THINK SHE --
I THINK SHE'S OD'ing.

1158
01:08:29,139 --> 01:08:30,106
-REALLY?! YOU THINK SO?!

1159
01:08:30,140 --> 01:08:31,308
-COME ON, LET ME IN!

1160
01:08:31,341 --> 01:08:33,210
-CARLA, OPEN THE GODDAMN DOOR!

1161
01:08:33,243 --> 01:08:34,611
-CARLA, HOW MANY DID YOU TAKE?

1162
01:08:34,644 --> 01:08:37,214
-BOYS SHOULDN'T BE
IN THE GIRLS' BATHROOM!

1163
01:08:37,247 --> 01:08:38,782
WHAT ON EARTH
IS GOING ON IN HERE?

1164
01:08:38,815 --> 01:08:41,551
YOUR BEHAVIOR IS COMPLETELY --
-[ RETCHING ]

1165
01:08:41,585 --> 01:08:43,787
-MM. OH, GOD.

1166
01:08:43,820 --> 01:08:45,422
WHAT IS WRONG WITH HER?
-UH...

1167
01:08:45,455 --> 01:08:47,757
-IS SHE PREGNANT?
-NO, SHE'S JUST REALLY SICK.

1168
01:08:47,791 --> 01:08:49,626
SHE SAID IT'S SOMETHING
FROM THE CAFETERIA.

1169
01:08:49,659 --> 01:08:51,895
-OH. ALL RIGHT.

1170
01:08:51,928 --> 01:08:53,363
I'M -- I'M GETTING THE NURSE.

1171
01:08:53,397 --> 01:08:55,432
-WE'LL GET HER CLEANED UP.
-MM-HMM.

1172
01:08:57,667 --> 01:09:00,069
-CARLA, YOU OKAY?

1173
01:09:00,103 --> 01:09:02,606
-I CAN'T DO THIS ANYMORE.
-YOU SHOULD CRAWL UNDER.

1174
01:09:02,639 --> 01:09:05,108
-CARLA, COME ON!

1175
01:09:05,141 --> 01:09:06,343
-[ CRYING ]

1176
01:09:06,376 --> 01:09:09,646
I DON'T WANT TO DO THIS ANYMORE.

1177
01:09:09,679 --> 01:09:12,849
[ CRYING ]
-WHY DID YOU HAVE TO DO THAT?

1178
01:09:12,882 --> 01:09:15,519
COME ON.

1179
01:09:15,552 --> 01:09:17,987
LET'S GO TO THE NURSE'S OFFICE,
ALL RIGHT?

1180
01:09:18,021 --> 01:09:20,156
LET'S GET YOU CLEANED UP.

1181
01:09:26,062 --> 01:09:28,465
YOU THINK SHE'LL BE OKAY?

1182
01:09:30,967 --> 01:09:33,670
-SHE'LL HAVE
A ROUGH COUPLE DAYS.

1183
01:09:44,748 --> 01:09:47,384
-I CAN'T HELP THINKING...

1184
01:09:48,752 --> 01:09:52,489
...HOW MUCH EASIER MY LIFE
WOULD BE IF SHE WAS NEVER
A PART OF IT.

1185
01:10:01,097 --> 01:10:04,401
WE'RE NEVER GONNA GET OUT
OF THIS.

1186
01:10:08,538 --> 01:10:09,639
-ALEX.

1187
01:10:09,673 --> 01:10:13,076
I WAS JUST ABOUT TO PUT THIS
IN YOUR MAILBOX.

1188
01:10:14,010 --> 01:10:16,346
-THANKS.
-THE SCHEDULE'S UP FOR NEXT WEEK

1189
01:10:16,380 --> 01:10:19,283
WHEN YOU GET A CHANCE
TO CHECK IT OUT.

1190
01:10:22,486 --> 01:10:24,588
-[ SCOFFS ]

1191
01:10:31,395 --> 01:10:33,863
I THINK I JUST FIGURED OUT A WAY

1192
01:10:33,897 --> 01:10:37,033
TO STEAL
A HALF A MILLION DOLLARS.

1193
01:10:43,773 --> 01:10:45,742
[ KNOCK ON DOOR ]

1194
01:10:52,582 --> 01:10:56,252
-CONVENIENT TIMING FOR SOMEBODY
TO GET FOOD POISONING.

1195
01:10:56,286 --> 01:10:57,954
-SHE TRIED TO KILL HERSELF.

1196
01:10:57,987 --> 01:10:59,689
-SHE COULDN'T EVEN DO THAT
RIGHT.

1197
01:10:59,723 --> 01:11:02,359
-SHUT UP, ALL RIGHT?
THAT'S NOT WHY WE CAME HERE.

1198
01:11:02,392 --> 01:11:04,694
LOOK, WE THINK
WE FIGURED SOMETHING OUT.

1199
01:11:04,728 --> 01:11:08,565
[ HIP-HOP MUSIC PLAYS
IN BACKGROUND ]

1200
01:11:08,598 --> 01:11:09,866
-$43.

1201
01:11:09,899 --> 01:11:11,435
-YOU MAKE FAKE I.D.s.

1202
01:11:11,468 --> 01:11:13,069
YOU THINK YOU CAN HANDLE
A PAYCHECK?

1203
01:11:13,102 --> 01:11:16,272
-YOU WANT ME TO MAKE
A TEACHER'S CHECK FOR $500,000?

1204
01:11:16,306 --> 01:11:17,974
COME ON, MAN!

1205
01:11:18,007 --> 01:11:21,311
-LOOK, THERE'S 46 WELD NATIONAL
BANKS WITHIN A 2-HOUR RADIUS.

1206
01:11:21,345 --> 01:11:23,947
WE NEED YOU TO MAKE 46 CHECKS
FOR DIFFERENT AMOUNTS

1207
01:11:23,980 --> 01:11:25,715
CLOSE TO BUT UNDER 10 GRAND.

1208
01:11:25,749 --> 01:11:27,250
-I DON'T GET IT.

1209
01:11:27,283 --> 01:11:30,387
-BANKS ONLY FLAG TRANSFERS
THAT ARE $10,000 OR MORE.

1210
01:11:32,956 --> 01:11:36,092
-WE JUST NEED
TO FILL THOSE DEPOSIT SLIPS OUT.

1211
01:11:36,926 --> 01:11:40,430
-GIVE FAUSTIN THE A.T.M. CARD.

1212
01:12:14,130 --> 01:12:17,634
[ HIP-HOP MUSIC CONTINUES ]

1213
01:12:40,189 --> 01:12:42,926
[ MUSIC CONTINUES ]

1214
01:13:25,469 --> 01:13:27,471
[ KEYBOARD CLACKING ]

1215
01:13:31,441 --> 01:13:34,110
-WE ACTUALLY DID IT.

1216
01:13:34,143 --> 01:13:37,013
AFTER WEEKS OF WORRYING
THAT OUR LIVES WERE OVER,

1217
01:13:37,046 --> 01:13:39,248
WE HAD THE KEYS TO OUR FREEDOM.

1218
01:13:50,126 --> 01:13:53,630
-PRINCIPAL DONATO, CAN YOU
COME MEET ME IN THE LIBRARY?

1219
01:13:57,901 --> 01:13:59,669
PRINCIPAL DONATO?

1220
01:13:59,703 --> 01:14:02,739
-Sure, I'll be right there.

1221
01:14:30,333 --> 01:14:31,801
[ DOOR OPENS ]

1222
01:14:43,880 --> 01:14:45,014
-WHAT'S GOING ON?

1223
01:14:45,048 --> 01:14:46,683
-I THINK WE HAVE A PROBLEM.

1224
01:14:46,716 --> 01:14:52,055
I NEED YOU TO LOG INTO THE
SCHOOL'S AUXILIARY ACCOUNT.

1225
01:15:13,509 --> 01:15:15,779
HMM. INTERESTING.

1226
01:15:17,781 --> 01:15:18,815
-ALL RIGHT?

1227
01:15:18,848 --> 01:15:21,084
-OKAY, THANK YOU.
THAT'LL BE ALL.

1228
01:15:31,761 --> 01:15:33,897
SO?

1229
01:15:50,446 --> 01:15:53,382
WHAT HAPPENED NEXT?

1230
01:15:57,821 --> 01:16:00,423
-WE TOLD FAUSTIN WHAT WE DID.

1231
01:16:00,456 --> 01:16:05,695
AND HE ASKED US TO MEET HIM
IN HIS CLASSROOM THAT NIGHT.

1232
01:16:17,974 --> 01:16:20,243
-HELLO?

1233
01:16:20,276 --> 01:16:21,344
[ DOOR CLOSES ]

1234
01:16:21,377 --> 01:16:24,848
-YOU KIDS HAVE SOMETHING FOR ME?

1235
01:16:30,654 --> 01:16:32,956
PUT THE CARD ON THE TABLE.

1236
01:16:43,466 --> 01:16:44,500
WHAT'S THE P.I.N.?

1237
01:16:44,533 --> 01:16:47,403
-8567.

1238
01:16:53,309 --> 01:16:56,579
-WELL...

1239
01:16:56,612 --> 01:16:59,883
I GUESS WE'RE DONE HERE.

1240
01:17:04,854 --> 01:17:07,891
-YOU GUESS WE'RE DONE HERE?
-LET IT GO, CAMERON.

1241
01:17:07,924 --> 01:17:09,993
-THAT'S -- THAT'S ALL
YOU HAVE TO SAY?

1242
01:17:10,026 --> 01:17:13,629
AFTER ALL THAT YOU
PUT US THROUGH, THAT'S IT?

1243
01:17:13,663 --> 01:17:15,564
-WALK AWAY, CAMERON.

1244
01:17:15,598 --> 01:17:17,333
-FUCK YOU!
-HEY, LET IT GO, CAMERON.

1245
01:17:17,366 --> 01:17:19,602
-NO! WE'RE NOT GONNA LET HIM
GET AWAY WITH THIS!

1246
01:17:19,635 --> 01:17:21,705
-HEY, JUST RELAX. IT'S OVER.
-NO, YOU RELAX!

1247
01:17:21,738 --> 01:17:23,372
LISTEN, YOU JUST
DON'T UNDERSTAND!

1248
01:17:23,406 --> 01:17:25,341
YOU CAN'T JUST
PUSH PEOPLE AROUND!
-HE'S GOT A GUN!

1249
01:17:25,374 --> 01:17:27,744
-[ SCREAMS ]
-GET OUT OF THE WAY!
HE'S GOT A GUN!

1250
01:17:27,777 --> 01:17:29,946
-JACK!
[ GUNSHOT ]

1251
01:17:29,979 --> 01:17:31,881
[ SCREAMING ]

1252
01:17:31,915 --> 01:17:34,884
-CAMERON, WATCH OUT!
-[ SCREAMING ]

1253
01:17:34,918 --> 01:17:37,987
JACK!
-[ GRUNTING ]

1254
01:17:38,021 --> 01:17:40,824
-CAMERON, WATCH OUT!
-WATCH OUT!

1255
01:17:40,857 --> 01:17:44,260
[ GUNSHOT ]
-[ GRUNTS ]

1256
01:17:44,293 --> 01:17:45,862
-WHAT'D YOU DO?!

1257
01:17:48,097 --> 01:17:51,534
-OW!

1258
01:17:51,567 --> 01:17:53,002
OH.

1259
01:17:53,036 --> 01:17:54,470
YOU --
-NO!

1260
01:17:54,503 --> 01:17:57,540
[ GUNSHOT ]

1261
01:17:57,573 --> 01:18:00,443
-OH!

1262
01:18:00,476 --> 01:18:02,345
-CARLA!
[ GUNSHOT ]

1263
01:18:02,378 --> 01:18:03,512
NO!
[ GUNSHOT ]

1264
01:18:03,546 --> 01:18:05,548
[ GRUNTS ]

1265
01:18:17,226 --> 01:18:18,995
-CAN YOU GET UP?

1266
01:18:19,028 --> 01:18:20,163
-JACK.

1267
01:18:20,196 --> 01:18:21,931
- I CAN'T FEEL MY LEGS.

1268
01:18:21,965 --> 01:18:24,367
[ GLASS BREAKING ]
-JACK, WE GOT TO GO.

1269
01:18:24,400 --> 01:18:26,635
JACK, WE GOT TO GO.

1270
01:18:29,172 --> 01:18:30,840
-IT'S FINE.

1271
01:18:30,874 --> 01:18:32,708
-YOU GOT TO GET OUT OF HERE.

1272
01:18:32,742 --> 01:18:35,011
-COME ON, JACK.

1273
01:18:39,015 --> 01:18:41,117
[ EXPLOSION ]

1274
01:18:47,190 --> 01:18:51,828
THEY FOUND ME IN THE HALLWAY,
AND THEY TOOK ME TO THE MEDICS.

1275
01:18:53,797 --> 01:18:57,033
I TOLD THE POLICE --

1276
01:18:58,501 --> 01:19:01,604
I TOLD THEM WHAT
THEY NEEDED TO KNOW.

1277
01:19:03,272 --> 01:19:06,642
-WELL, YOU DIDN'T TELL THEM
THE WHOLE STORY.

1278
01:19:08,477 --> 01:19:11,347
YOU WERE PUSHED TO
YOUR BREAKING POINT
BY A VERY SICK MAN,

1279
01:19:11,380 --> 01:19:14,450
BUT THAT DOESN'T MEAN
YOU WERE INNOCENT.

1280
01:19:14,483 --> 01:19:15,684
WHAT?

1281
01:19:15,718 --> 01:19:19,956
YOU STOLE, CHEATED, LIED.

1282
01:19:19,989 --> 01:19:21,958
IF A JURY HEARD
WHAT YOU JUST TOLD ME

1283
01:19:21,991 --> 01:19:24,193
AND SAW THAT YOU
WERE THE ONLY SURVIVOR...

1284
01:19:24,227 --> 01:19:26,295
YOU WOULD GO TO JAIL.

1285
01:19:27,730 --> 01:19:29,732
-I DID WHAT I HAD TO DO.

1286
01:19:29,765 --> 01:19:32,869
-PEOPLE LOST THEIR LIVES, ALEX.

1287
01:19:32,902 --> 01:19:35,771
-I THOUGHT YOU SAID THIS THING
WAS CONFIDENTIAL.

1288
01:19:35,805 --> 01:19:38,041
-DO YOU REALLY THINK THAT A JURY
WILL SYMPATHIZE WITH YOU?

1289
01:19:38,074 --> 01:19:40,643
-WE WERE VICTIMS.
YOU SAID IT YOURSELF.

1290
01:19:40,676 --> 01:19:44,848
-I CAN PROVE
THAT YOU ROBBED THE SCHOOL
OF A HALF-MILLION DOLLARS.

1291
01:19:45,849 --> 01:19:49,518
[ CHUCKLES ]
DIDN'T YOU?

1292
01:19:49,552 --> 01:19:51,754
YOU'RE PATHETIC.

1293
01:19:51,787 --> 01:19:55,758
-WHAT ARE YOU GONNA DO TO ME?

1294
01:19:55,791 --> 01:19:59,062
-I'M NOT GONNA DO ANYTHING
TO YOU.

1295
01:20:02,131 --> 01:20:05,668
-SO, WHAT DO YOU WANT?
[ SNIFFLES ]

1296
01:20:06,970 --> 01:20:09,805
-I WANT YOU TO LEAVE...

1297
01:20:09,839 --> 01:20:11,574
AND NEVER COME BACK.

1298
01:20:11,607 --> 01:20:16,880
I WANT YOU TO NEVER SPEAK OF THE
EVENTS OF THESE LAST FEW WEEKS

1299
01:20:16,913 --> 01:20:19,115
TO ANYONE AS LONG AS YOU LIVE.

1300
01:20:19,148 --> 01:20:22,018
BECAUSE IF YOU DO,
I WILL COME AFTER YOU,

1301
01:20:22,051 --> 01:20:25,288
AND NEXT TIME,
I WILL NOT BE SO GENEROUS.

1302
01:20:34,964 --> 01:20:38,201
YOUR TRANSFER
SHOULD BE READY NOW.

1303
01:20:45,341 --> 01:20:46,742
-SIGN RIGHT HERE.

1304
01:20:46,775 --> 01:20:49,778
I'VE ARRANGED A NICE NEW HOME
FOR YOU IN A GOOD SCHOOL SYSTEM.

1305
01:20:49,812 --> 01:20:51,347
RIGHT HERE, PLEASE.

1306
01:20:52,615 --> 01:20:56,585
YOU -- YOU HAVE A RIDE HOME?

1307
01:20:56,619 --> 01:20:59,122
A CAR, YEAH?

1308
01:20:59,155 --> 01:21:03,126
UM, WELL, I THINK
THAT'S ABOUT IT.

1309
01:21:03,159 --> 01:21:06,896
HOPEFULLY, YOU CAN PUT THIS
WHOLE THING BEHIND YOU SOON.

1310
01:21:09,298 --> 01:21:11,901
GOOD LUCK, ALEX.

1311
01:21:26,349 --> 01:21:28,417
SO, UH, ALL IS WELL?

1312
01:21:30,653 --> 01:21:34,590
-ALEX THOMAS
WILL NEVER TALK ABOUT WHAT
HAPPENED LAST NIGHT AGAIN.

1313
01:21:34,623 --> 01:21:36,892
-WELL, THANK GOD FOR THAT.

1314
01:21:36,926 --> 01:21:38,794
WHAT ABOUT THE MONEY?

1315
01:21:38,827 --> 01:21:40,829
-WE NEED TO DISSOLVE
THE ACCOUNT.

1316
01:21:40,863 --> 01:21:43,132
SO, WE HAVE TO FIGURE OUT
WHERE TO PUT IT.

1317
01:21:43,166 --> 01:21:46,535
-[ SIGHS ]

1318
01:21:47,603 --> 01:21:49,772
-THIS IS THE FILE
ON BRITTANY YOU ASKED FOR.

1319
01:21:49,805 --> 01:21:52,075
-OH, THANK YOU.

1320
01:22:04,420 --> 01:22:06,089
[ COMPUTER DINGS ]

1321
01:22:06,122 --> 01:22:09,258
-"MESSAGE
FROM BRITTANY TAMMAND."

1322
01:22:09,292 --> 01:22:10,926
-WHAT?

1323
01:22:10,960 --> 01:22:12,728
-I DON'T UNDERSTAND.

1324
01:22:12,761 --> 01:22:15,198
WHO SENT THIS?

1325
01:22:18,701 --> 01:22:20,369
-IS THAT BRITTANY?

1326
01:22:20,403 --> 01:22:21,237
-UH-HUH

1327
01:22:21,270 --> 01:22:23,906
-I DIDN'T KNOW WHAT TO DO.

1328
01:22:25,908 --> 01:22:28,311
HE TOLD ME.

1329
01:22:28,344 --> 01:22:31,014
[ CRIES SOFTLY ]

1330
01:22:31,047 --> 01:22:34,984
IT SOUNDS SO STUPID
WHEN I SAY IT OUT LOUD.

1331
01:22:35,018 --> 01:22:37,553
HE WAS THE MOST POPULAR GUY
AT SCHOOL,

1332
01:22:37,586 --> 01:22:39,688
AND HE TOLD ME
THAT HE LOVED ME.

1333
01:22:39,722 --> 01:22:43,259
[ CRIES ]

1334
01:22:43,292 --> 01:22:45,394
